Package me.marcosassuncao.servsim.profile

Class RangeList

java.lang.Object
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.profile.RangeList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Comparable<RangeList>, Iterable<Range>
public class RangeList extends Object implements Cloneable, Iterable<Range>, Comparable<RangeList>
This class represents a list of Range's. This is used to represent the ranges of resources used by a request and by the allocation policies to create a profile of ranges available at particular simulation times.
Author:
Marcos Dias de Assuncao
